title: Sports Briefing | Tennis: Venus Williams Into Semifinals
text:
Published By: NYTimes Tennis - Today 
Venus Williams advanced to the semifinals of the Wuhan Open in China by beating Johanna Konta, 6-4, 3-6, 7-5, on Thursday....
